{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":568360,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":118524,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这种得公开向全校同学道歉吧，恢复名誉","timestamp":1605675169,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":568370,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":118524,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: dz也觉得，不一定要官方途径，但是在pyq\u0026树洞公开正式的道歉信是必要的","timestamp":1605675223,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":568371,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":118524,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我觉得需要在公开场合或者至少能确保道歉传达给公众，这就是名誉权侵权了，至少得把对该同学声誉造成的损害抹平","timestamp":1605675245,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":568377,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":118524,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不管用什么方法至少要让所有因为这个事件对该同学人品产生误解的同学知道事情并非如此","timestamp":1605675313,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":568389,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":118524,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"建议小学弟起诉这个憨批，让她经历下名声败坏的痛苦！","timestamp":1605675455,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":118524,"reply":5,"tag":null,"text":"希望在有确切证据前不要消费大家的正义感\n不仅对被冤枉的当事人是伤害\n对以后可能遭遇类似事情的人也是伤害\n希望这位同学向被自己冤枉的c同学严肃道歉","timestamp":1605675131,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782653,"url":"","vote":{}}}